Hector Morejon, 19, was shot by a Long Beach, California, police officer, who allegedly thought the 19-year-old was pointing a gun at him during a trespassing and vandalism incident .
His mother, Lucia, was at home when she heard the shots and realized it was her son in the ambulance .
She went to an alley to see what happened but was not given any information .
Her attorney Sonia Mercado said: 'He was reaching for her - reaching out to her for help'